headline: Regions Financial Corp. Announces Common Stock Repurchase Program
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., December 10, 2025--Regions Financial Corp. announced its Board of Directors authorized the repurchase of up to $3.0 billion of the company’s common stock.
